The paper discusses the application of machine learning algorithms to medical image analysis, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of crowdsourcing for creating large-scale datasets is a human-computer interaction (cs.HC) topic. The paper also discusses the challenges and considerations of using crowdsourcing, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses future opportunities for development, which could fall under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
